By":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />I know that feel <br />\n唯有希望無事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"依加眼都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有經驗？<br />\n<br />\n⼁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDPv16U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDPv16U.png&h=07a3b9a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"認真,可能過唔到今晚"},{"pid":"da2c6e550e59aaf6ce80f9f83b8a876b12077337","tid":2124734,"uid":292796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"即刻睇醫生啦.. 生命尼"},{"pid":"031a2167d83397b358607ac61f2b685f261230f3","tid":2124734,"uid":252264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad5b250450359d53bd8b7324e41aa3a19601e46c","tid":2124734,"uid":71915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02caaaa96be2a7b3efd08a10214c708e56a3dfe5","tid":2124734,"uid":40388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"呢間雖然唔係好好但開廿四 打去問下啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWB6Aof.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWB6Aof.png&h=04ac9d54&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"呢間啲評價好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"全港睇鼠得佢有24 <br />\n之前鼠鼠心臟病 睇楓樹果間 <br />\n都話有咩事要去大圍 等唔到第日先搵佢地<br />\n起碼救起左先 <br />\n<br />\n你自己諗啦 睇佢張相咁無生命力<br />\n越快睇就越好"},{"pid":"8c98b94b119c5bb258e47940769ff8dd57dce598","tid":2124734,"uid":47980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T22:23:31.000Z","msg":"荃灣享和 大角咀楓樹 ： 相對平 都OK <br />\n天后星寵：好貴 但超級好 負擔到首選<br />\n大圍 ：又貴又唔好 係24小時吊命先去"},{"pid":"6039bfc69aba837de490eb51196eb96471c03b09","tid":2124734,"uid":233015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T22:36:04.000Z","msg":"佢連瓜子都唔食？<br />\n菜呢？ <br />\n如果好急先去大圍，平時去返享和楓樹"},{"pid":"81023a33a01546836ff90daf561bd835d3b9cb28","tid":2124734,"uid":255489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"樓主帶左隻鼠睇醫生未?依家楓樹甚至當日都有位去睇，唔算好貴。隻鼠咁樣唔拖得"},{"pid":"c540e953fda0dcedf4efd02cc53f5edc49887953","tid":2124734,"uid":6480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"帶佢醫生未呀?"},{"pid":"d604616a6911862e3ea01c1644752c83e7caed5f","tid":2124734,"uid":71915,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c540e953fda0dcedf4efd02cc53f5edc49887953","tid":2124734,"uid":6480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"帶佢醫生未呀?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"已帶左睇醫生 話濕尾<br />\n<br />\n但係最後都挨唔過<br />\n<br />\n牙牙 唔會再辛苦啦<br />\n<br />\n過左彩虹橋之後 要乖乖地 唔會再辛苦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗再肚屙 唔洗再食唔到野 唔洗再飲唔到水<br />\n<br />\n你係唯一一隻牙牙鼠<br />\n<br />\n我同媽媽以後都唔會買鼠啦<br />\n<br />\n你下世要健康成長 快高長大<br />\n<br />\nLove You <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQQOVr8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQQOVr8.png&h=1a7e9532&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fc4035a38667eaa036787ac103d143d1a9d6001","tid":2124734,"uid":6480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d604616a6911862e3ea01c1644752c83e7caed5f","tid":2124734,"uid":71915,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c540e953fda0dcedf4efd02cc53f5edc49887953","tid":2124734,"uid":6480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"帶佢醫生未呀?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"已帶左睇醫生 話濕尾<br />\n<br />\n但係最後都挨唔過<br />\n<br />\n牙牙 唔會再辛苦啦<br />\n<br />\n過左彩虹橋之後 要乖乖地 唔會再辛苦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗再肚屙 唔洗再食唔到野 唔洗再飲唔到水<br />\n<br />\n你係唯一一隻牙牙鼠<br />\n<br />\n我同媽媽以後都唔會買鼠啦<br />\n<br />\n你下世要健康成長 快高長